GIT Commands : 

Git init
git add <file>
git Status
git commit

git push  --> for remote repo
git pull  
git clone --> copy remote repo to local folder


git config --global user.name  '___'
git config --global user.email '___'

git add index.html  ---> for add in local repo
git status --> check that status
git rm --cached index.html  --> remove that file from repo
git status
git add *.html  --> we can add any html of this folder
git add .  --> for all files (we generaly use)
git commit or git commit -m "---"

git status --> nothing to commit

git branch <branch name>
git checkout <branch name>
git merge  branch '__branch name_to_current_'



git remote ad origin https://----git repo add---
git push -u origin master




